THE DESTINED PATH

Denmark, Aarhus, 1989.
Martin Due is born.

Neighbor's house, 1995.
Martin beats Super Mario 3. with a friend which leads to a serious addiction.

Risskov, 1999.
Big brother teaches Martin english during a memorable playthrough of Zelda: Ocarina of Time.

Aarhus School of Engineering, 11111011011.
Endless combinations of digital bits enters Martin's array of vision and soon he finds himself in dismay.

Copenhagen, 2013.
Martin stumples through hell in the late of night and finally defeats Spelunky. Then most of his hair falls of.

Aarhus, 2014.
In a long shower Martin's brain twitches a bit. Minutes later magic appears on screen.

Oregon, 2015.
As he grabs a dark piece, Martin realizes that obsidian has finally made its way out of Terraria. Meanwhile Jonathan drops his cupcake.

Washington, 2015. 
The meaning of Braid enlightens Martin's thoughts for a week. He makes a terrible decision.

Aarhus, 2016.
Martin starts his own game studio and tries to take over the world. 